---
// About.astro
---

<section id="about" class="py-20 bg-gradient-to-br from-gray-900 via-gray-800 to-gray-900 relative overflow-hidden">
  <!-- Background elements -->
  <div class="absolute inset-0 opacity-5">
    <div class="absolute top-1/4 left-1/4 w-96 h-96 bg-cyan-500 rounded-full blur-3xl"></div>
    <div class="absolute bottom-1/4 right-1/4 w-96 h-96 bg-blue-500 rounded-full blur-3xl"></div>
  </div>
  
  <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8 relative z-10">
    <!-- Section Header -->
    <div class="text-center mb-16">
      <h2 class="text-4xl lg:text-5xl font-bold text-white mb-4">
        <span class="bg-gradient-to-r from-cyan-400 to-blue-600 bg-clip-text text-transparent">
          Sobre mí
        </span>
      </h2>
      <div class="w-24 h-1 bg-gradient-to-r from-cyan-400 to-blue-600 mx-auto mb-6"></div>
      <p class="text-xl text-gray-300 max-w-3xl mx-auto">
        Ingeniero en Sistemas Computacionales especializado en ciberseguridad y Hacking Ético.
      </p>
    </div>

    <div class="grid lg:grid-cols-2 gap-12 items-center">
      <!-- Left side - Personal info -->
      <div class="space-y-8">
        <div class="bg-gray-800/50 backdrop-blur-sm rounded-xl p-8 border border-cyan-500/20 hover:border-cyan-500/40 transition-all duration-300">
          <h3 class="text-2xl font-bold text-white mb-6 flex items-center">
            <svg class="w-6 h-6 text-cyan-400 mr-3" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
              <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M16 7a4 4 0 11-8 0 4 4 0 018 0zM12 14a7 7 0 00-7 7h14a7 7 0 00-7-7z"/>
            </svg>
            Mi historia
          </h3>
          <p class="text-gray-300 leading-relaxed mb-6">
            Soy Ingeniero en Sistemas Computacionales con sólida experiencia en ciberseguridad y desarrollo de software. 
            Mi pasión por el aprendizaje continuo y la mejora de la seguridad digital me ha llevado a contribuir activamente 
            en la comunidad internacional de hacking ético, donde facilito formación gratuita y mentoría a personas de todas las edades.
          </p>
          <p class="text-gray-300 leading-relaxed">
            Mi enfoque se basa en el pensamiento crítico, la ética digital y la creación de soluciones tecnológicas efectivas. 
            He impactado a más de 150 estudiantes a través de formación gratuita, desarrollando proyectos que van desde 
            plataformas educativas hasta herramientas de automatización y pentesting.
          </p>
        </div>

        <!-- Skills progression -->
        <div class="bg-gray-800/50 backdrop-blur-sm rounded-xl p-8 border border-cyan-500/20 hover:border-cyan-500/40 transition-all duration-300">
          <h3 class="text-2xl font-bold text-white mb-6 flex items-center">
            <svg class="w-6 h-6 text-cyan-400 mr-3" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
              <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M13 10V3L4 14h7v7l9-11h-7z"/>
            </svg>
            Especialidades
          </h3>
          <div class="space-y-4">
            <div class="flex items-center justify-between">
              <span class="text-gray-300">Pentesting & Ciberseguridad</span>
              <span class="text-cyan-400 font-semibold">95%</span>
            </div>
            <div class="w-full bg-gray-700 rounded-full h-2">
              <div class="bg-gradient-to-r from-cyan-400 to-blue-600 h-2 rounded-full w-[95%]"></div>
            </div>
            
            <div class="flex items-center justify-between">
              <span class="text-gray-300">Python & Automatización</span>
              <span class="text-cyan-400 font-semibold">90%</span>
            </div>
            <div class="w-full bg-gray-700 rounded-full h-2">
              <div class="bg-gradient-to-r from-cyan-400 to-blue-600 h-2 rounded-full w-[90%]"></div>
            </div>
            
            <div class="flex items-center justify-between">
              <span class="text-gray-300">Desarrollo Web</span>
              <span class="text-cyan-400 font-semibold">85%</span>
            </div>
            <div class="w-full bg-gray-700 rounded-full h-2">
              <div class="bg-gradient-to-r from-cyan-400 to-blue-600 h-2 rounded-full w-[85%]"></div>
            </div>
            
            <div class="flex items-center justify-between">
              <span class="text-gray-300">Mentoría & Enseñanza</span>
              <span class="text-cyan-400 font-semibold">92%</span>
            </div>
            <div class="w-full bg-gray-700 rounded-full h-2">
              <div class="bg-gradient-to-r from-cyan-400 to-blue-600 h-2 rounded-full w-[92%]"></div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- Right side - Technical skills -->
      <div class="space-y-8">
        <!-- Tech stack -->
        <div class="bg-gray-800/50 backdrop-blur-sm rounded-xl p-8 border border-cyan-500/20 hover:border-cyan-500/40 transition-all duration-300">
          <h3 class="text-2xl font-bold text-white mb-6 flex items-center">
            <svg class="w-6 h-6 text-cyan-400 mr-3" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
              <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M10 20l4-16m4 4l4 4-4 4M6 16l-4-4 4-4"/>
            </svg>
            Stack Tecnológico
          </h3>
          <div class="grid grid-cols-2 gap-4">
            <div class="space-y-3">
              <h4 class="text-cyan-400 font-semibold">Ciberseguridad</h4>
              <div class="flex flex-wrap gap-2">
                <span class="px-3 py-1 bg-red-500/20 text-red-400 rounded-full text-sm border border-red-500/30">
                  Pentesting
                </span>
                <span class="px-3 py-1 bg-red-500/20 text-red-400 rounded-full text-sm border border-red-500/30">
                  OSINT
                </span>
                <span class="px-3 py-1 bg-red-500/20 text-red-400 rounded-full text-sm border border-red-500/30">
                  Burp Suite
                </span>
                <span class="px-3 py-1 bg-red-500/20 text-red-400 rounded-full text-sm border border-red-500/30">
                  Metasploit
                </span>
              </div>
            </div>
            <div class="space-y-3">
              <h4 class="text-cyan-400 font-semibold">Programación</h4>
              <div class="flex flex-wrap gap-2">
                <span class="px-3 py-1 bg-green-500/20 text-green-400 rounded-full text-sm border border-green-500/30">
                  Python
                </span>
                <span class="px-3 py-1 bg-green-500/20 text-green-400 rounded-full text-sm border border-green-500/30">
                  JavaScript
                </span>
                <span class="px-3 py-1 bg-green-500/20 text-green-400 rounded-full text-sm border border-green-500/30">
                  Node.js
                </span>
                <span class="px-3 py-1 bg-green-500/20 text-green-400 rounded-full text-sm border border-green-500/30">
                  React
                </span>
              </div>
            </div>
            <div class="space-y-3">
              <h4 class="text-cyan-400 font-semibold">Sistemas</h4>
              <div class="flex flex-wrap gap-2">
                <span class="px-3 py-1 bg-blue-500/20 text-blue-400 rounded-full text-sm border border-blue-500/30">
                  Linux
                </span>
                <span class="px-3 py-1 bg-blue-500/20 text-blue-400 rounded-full text-sm border border-blue-500/30">
                  Windows
                </span>
                <span class="px-3 py-1 bg-blue-500/20 text-blue-400 rounded-full text-sm border border-blue-500/30">
                  Docker
                </span>
                <span class="px-3 py-1 bg-blue-500/20 text-blue-400 rounded-full text-sm border border-blue-500/30">
                  PostgreSQL
                </span>
              </div>
            </div>
            <div class="space-y-3">
              <h4 class="text-cyan-400 font-semibold">Herramientas</h4>
              <div class="flex flex-wrap gap-2">
                <span class="px-3 py-1 bg-purple-500/20 text-purple-400 rounded-full text-sm border border-purple-500/30">
                  Wireshark
                </span>
                <span class="px-3 py-1 bg-purple-500/20 text-purple-400 rounded-full text-sm border border-purple-500/30">
                  Nmap
                </span>
                <span class="px-3 py-1 bg-purple-500/20 text-purple-400 rounded-full text-sm border border-purple-500/30">
                  Git
                </span>
                <span class="px-3 py-1 bg-purple-500/20 text-purple-400 rounded-full text-sm border border-purple-500/30">
                  Bash
                </span>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>

        <!-- Certificates/Achievements -->
        <div class="bg-gray-800/50 backdrop-blur-sm rounded-xl p-8 border border-cyan-500/20 hover:border-cyan-500/40 transition-all duration-300">
          <h3 class="text-2xl font-bold text-white mb-6 flex items-center">
            <svg class="w-6 h-6 text-cyan-400 mr-3" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24"></svg>
              <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M9 12l2 2 4-4m5.618-4.016A11.955 11.955 0 0112 2.944a11.955 11.955 0 01-8.618 3.04A12.02 12.02 0 003 9c0 5.591 3.824 10.29 9 11.622 5.176-1.332 9-6.03 9-11.622 0-1.042-.133-2.052-.382-3.016z"/>
            </svg>
            Logros y Experiencia
          </h3>
          <div class="space-y-4">
            <div class="flex items-start space-x-3">
              

              <br>
              <br>
              <div>
                <h4 class="text-white font-semibold">Auditor HackerOne y en Entornos realistas</h4>
                <p class="text-gray-300 text-sm">Identificación de vulnerabilidades críticas en sistemas, aplicaciones web y dispositivos en entornos reales pero propios y controlados</p>
              </div>
            </div>
            <br>
            <div class="flex items-start space-x-3">
             <br>
              <div>
                <h4 class="text-white font-semibold">Formador Internacional</h4>
                <p class="text-gray-300 text-sm">+150 estudiantes impactados con formación gratuita en hacking ético, programación y más</p>
              </div>
            </div>
            
           <br>
              <div>
                <h4 class="text-white font-semibold">Certificaciones</h4>
                <p class="text-gray-300 text-sm">CRTA, ECHA, Auditor de Seguridad, LODPD, Microsoft Git, Python, Fullstack y más</p>
              </div>
            </div>
            <br>
         
              <div>
                <h4 class="text-white font-semibold">Proyectos Destacados</h4>
                <p class="text-gray-300 text-sm">Plataforma educativa, mini-lab pentesting, Cursos de Pentesting, Cursos Intensivos de diversos áreas, herramientas de Hacking y más</p>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>


</section>

<style>
  /* Animaciones sutiles para los elementos */
  @keyframes fadeInUp {
    from {
      opacity: 0;
      transform: translateY(30px);
    }
    to {
      opacity: 1;
      transform: translateY(0);
    }
  }

  /* Efecto hover para las tarjetas */
  .bg-gray-800\/50:hover {
    transform: translateY(-5px);
    box-shadow: 0 20px 40px rgba(6, 182, 212, 0.1);
  }

  /* Animación para las barras de progreso */
  .bg-gradient-to-r {
    animation: progressBar 2s ease-in-out;
  }

  @keyframes progressBar {
    from { width: 0%; }
    to { width: var(--progress-width); }
  }
</style>